{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Walking Trade</strong> is a quirky, action-packed zombie apocalypse store management game where chaos and commerce collide!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/TWT_RunTheShopTitle.png?t=1734089406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Design your shop, balancing space, aesthetics, and functionality. Organize shelves, set prices, and ensure customers leave happy - or at least alive.<i>  </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i></i><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/StackingShelvesGif_1.gif?t=1734089406\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/TWT_ProtectTitle.png?t=1734089406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customers aren\u2019t your only problem - zombies invade! Wield melee weapons, firearms, or whatever you can find to defend your shop during raids and hordes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/ZombieHordeGif_1.gif?t=1734089406\" /><i></i><strong></strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/TWT_ManageTitle.png?t=1734089406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hire survivors to scavenge supplies, serve customers, or guard the shop. Keep them equipped and motivated to reap the rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/ManageStaffGif.gif?t=1734089406\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/TWT_CraftTitle.png?t=1734089406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock crafting stations to create weapons, tools, and shop upgrades. Build barricades, storage units, and even makeshift traps to keep zombies at bay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/CraftingGif.gif?t=1734089406\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/TWT_KillCustomerTitle.png?t=1734089406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be a benevolent shopkeeper or an opportunistic overlord. Help the community, price gouge, or even sabotage settlements for profit. Your reputation determines who comes knocking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/extras/KillCustomerGif.gif?t=1734089406\" /><i></i><br>In <strong>The Walking Trade</strong>, every decision shapes your survival. Build, fight, and thrive in the apocalypse\u2014your way!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734089406","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/page.bg.jpg?t=1734089406","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/48f01481c0928d89f6a905143f5b3a327226b42f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734089406","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398110/48f01481c0928d89f6a905143f5b3a327226b42f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734089406","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Walking Trade</strong> is a quirky, action-packed zombie apocalypse store management game where chaos and commerce collide!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img c